*   **The Golden Ratio of Negative Space (قاعدة المساحة الفارغة):**
    *   *The Rule:* At least 60% of the cover must be completely devoid of text or active graphic elements.
    *   *The Front Cover Blueprint:* The book title sits elegantly in the upper third. The author name sits in the bottom third. The center holds a single, highly artistic, and abstract symbolic asset (e.g., a quiet, stone-textured archway) surrounded by vast, clean parchment background.
